de poesia juntas.

284
00:18:21,559 --> 00:18:23,778
- E daí?
- E daí?

285
00:18:23,936 --> 00:18:25,734
Poesia?

286
00:18:25,896 --> 00:18:28,115
Susan é lésbica.

287
00:18:28,274 --> 00:18:30,618
