- Sim.

333
00:21:17,526 --> 00:21:19,824
Eu vou contar a
Frank e Alice agora mesmo.

334
00:21:19,987 --> 00:21:21,204
Certo.

335
00:21:22,281 --> 00:21:24,500
- Tchau, Pheebs.
- Tchau.

